    This blog is used to record my learning notes, project experiences, and occasional thoughts.
  </p>
  <p>
    You can find some related links below. Feel free to reach out and connect.
  </p>
  <Button title='Sponsor Me' class='w-fit' href='/projects#sponsorship' variant='ahead' />

  <!-- #region 社交媒体 -->
